video.title: Dinner for Five
video.synopsis: In each episode, four celebrities join host Jon Favreau for dinner and share revealing stories about both show business and their personal lives.

episodes.synopsis: Join host Jon Favreau and the cast of "Vince Vaughn's Wild West Comedy Show" for a special 50th episode of the Emmy-nominated series "Dinner for Five."
episodes.title: Vince Vaughn's Wild West Comedy Show
